### Step 3 — Server Actions
**New file:** `src/lib/actions/projects/approval.ts`

Four exported functions following the pattern of existing actions (see `src/lib/actions/milestones/update-milestone.ts`):

| Function | Role | DB operation | Activity action |
|---|---|---|---|
| `giveAdminApproval(projectId)` | requireAdmin | `admin_approved=true, approved_by_admin=user.id, admin_approved_at=now()` | `admin_final_approval` |
| `revokeAdminApproval(projectId)` | requireAdmin | `admin_approved=false, approved_by_admin=null, admin_approved_at=null` (trigger auto-reverts status) | `admin_approval_revoked` |
| `adminApproveAndFinalize(projectId)` | requireAdmin | Both approval fields + `status='completed'` in one UPDATE | `admin_final_approval` + `project_finalized` |
| `finalizeProject(projectId)` | requireTeamMember | `status='completed'` (trigger blocks if not approved) | `project_finalized` |

All use `createServerClient()` (user JWT) so `auth.uid()` is correct in the trigger. Activity logging uses `logActivity()` from `src/lib/actions/activity.ts`.

Revalidate: `/admin/projects/${projectId}`, `/team/projects/${projectId}`, `/admin/projects`.

