### Step 6 — Team Member UI Component
**New file:** `src/app/team/projects/[id]/FinalizeProjectPanel.tsx`

`'use client'` component receiving `project`.

Render logic (only when `project.status === 'final_review'`):
- **`admin_approved = false`:** Disabled `"Finalize Project"` button, badge `Pending Admin Approval` (orange). Add a `title` tooltip: `"Waiting for admin final approval"`.
- **`admin_approved = true`:** Active `"Finalize Project"` button (calls `finalizeProject`), badge `Approved by {approver.full_name}` (green).

**Wire into:** `src/app/team/projects/[id]/page.tsx` — render `<FinalizeProjectPanel project={project} />` in the header area (below the status badge) when status is `final_review`.

